## Category Performance Analysis

### Revenue by Category

| Category         |  Revenue |
| ---------------- | -------: |
| Fashion          | ₹944,788 |
| Electronics      | ₹722,105 |
| Home & Kitchen   | ₹455,047 |
| Sports & Fitness | ₹421,643 |
| Beauty & Health  | ₹306,226 |

### Insights

* Fashion contributes the highest share of total revenue.
* Electronics is the second-largest revenue contributor.
* Beauty & Health represents the smallest category by revenue.

### Recommendation

* Continue expanding Fashion and Electronics offerings.
* Evaluate opportunities to increase sales in Beauty & Health through promotions and product diversification.

